cc:Work.dc:title: Elvie #135
cc:Work.dc:description:
[Panel 1: Elvie is assembling a Framework laptop kit. James is sitting opposite]
Elvie: I've bought a Framework laptop. It's modular, so I can change the motherboard without replacing the chassis.
James: Because it's better for the environment?
[Panel 2: The view has changed so that we can now see the open lid of Elvie's laptop, covered in stickers for various geeky companies, computer programs and more]
Elvie: No… So I can upgrade without losing my collection of stickers!
